        <num>CCP 4202</num>
        <heading>4202.  General duties of undertutor</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 4202.  General duties of undertutor
The undertutor shall express his concurrence or nonconcurrence in action suggested by the tutor to the court, as set forth in Article 4271, and shall act for the minor whenever the minor's interest is opposed to that of the tutor.</p>
        </content>
